Generation Summary Page (Import Shared Library Wizard)

Requires: Base Development System

Use this page of the Import Shared Library wizard to review a summary of the shared library import. Select Tools»Import»Shared Library to launch the Import Shared Library wizard.

This page includes the following component:

  • Generation Summary—Shows a summary of the functions for which the wizard generates wrapper VIs, where it saves them, and the type of error handling you selected.
